0.9.0.name: wordpress/ps-google-website-optimizer-setting
0.9.0.description:
"PS google website optimizer setting" is a plugin to set the scripts of Google Website Optimizer. It can change the pages and content to test and also set publishing date by the administration page of your WordPress.

Functions

  • Automatic output of scripts
  • Import of contents
  • Set testing date

Version History

  • 0.9.5
    • Bugfix : create database. check the security.
  • 0.9.0
    • Public release
